node.text: Trying to bring some laughter on a stressful election night. I present...Paul’s mom at virtual parent teacher conferences. Paul has opted to learn at home this year. Enjoy!

node.title: Paul’s Mom at Virtual Parent-Teacher Conferences

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 02, 2021. May be a meme of 1 person and text that says 'Teachers sitting down to take the same six SafeSchools virtual classes that we have to take every year: @teachertrauma Not this shit again. STARZ'.

node.text:
I know it’s important but can they at least update the modules?! In the bullying one, they’re still calling each other “dweeb” and shit 😂
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teachermemes #teachersofig #teacherlife #teacherproblems #teacherstyle

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Trauma on August 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'My students every time I try to introduce something new and innovative to our routine: @teachertrauma IT'S NEW AND I HATE IT'.

node.text:
I find that most kids aren’t a big fan of change 😂 Just have to push through that resistance!
.
.
.
.
#teach #teacher #teachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersfollowteachers #teacherproblems #teacherlife #teachermemes #teacherhumor #teachersofig
